original_title: The Game That Changed Football | Barcelona vs Real Madrid - UFEA Women’s Champions League
overview: On March 30, 2022, Barcelona and Real Madrid's rivalry was at the forefront of football. But this time, it was the women's teams who were centre stage as they played out a seven-goal thriller in front of a world record crowd of 91,553 fans.
title: The Game That Changed Football | Barcelona vs Real Madrid - UFEA Women’s Champions League
